	‚Ä¢	JSON Export of the Codex: Converting the spreadsheet data into a structured JSON format would be highly beneficial for integration with other systems (for example, feeding into an application, a website, or an ENFT minting process). Each sheet could become a JSON array of objects, with keys for each field. For instance, the BLEU_SYMBOL_MODULES sheet could be exported as an array of objects like:

